			I'm a <span class="font-black text-orange-600">technical lead</span> and <span class="font-black text-orange-600">fullstack developer</span> with over 10 years building Android and iOS apps, and more recently diving deep into <span class="font-black text-orange-600">Go microservices</span> and <span class="font-black text-orange-600">DevOps</span>. Based in beautiful Bergen, Norway, I'm a developer, husband, dad to three amazing kids, and someone who gets genuinely excited about clean code and well-architected systems.
		</p>
		<p class="py-2">
